s among the most terrifying and hateful spirits haunting the Shadow Isles. He has existed for countless centuries, shielded from true death by necromantic sorcery and the force of his own dark will. Those who dare face Mordekaiser in battle risk a horrific curse: he enslaves his victims\' souls to become instruments of destruction.','na','6.5.1'),(82,'Mordekaiser','the Iron Revenant','Shadow Isles','Mordekaiser','\'\'All things must die... and yet I live on.\'\'<br><br>The baleful revenant Mordekaiser is among the most terrifying and hateful spirits haunting the Shadow Isles. He has existed for countless centuries, shielded from true death by necromantic sorcery and the force of his own dark will. Those who dare face Mordekaiser in battle risk a horrific curse: he enslaves his victims\' souls to become instruments of destruction.','na','6.8.1'),(82,'Mordekaiser','the Iron Revenant','Shadow Isles','Mordekaiser','\'\'All things must die... and yet I live on.\'\'<br><br>The baleful revenant Mordekaiser is among the most terrifying and hateful spirits haunting the Shadow Isles. He has existed for countless centuries, shielded from true death by necromantic sorcery and the force of his own dark will. Those who dare face Mordekaiser in battle risk a horrific curse: he enslaves his victims\' souls to become instruments of destruction.','na','6.9.1'),(83,'Yorick','o Coveiro','Ilha das Sombras','Yorick','Uma criatura trágica e aterrorizante, Yorick é um ser fantasmagórico que existe no limiar da mortalidade. Alguns dizem que ele foi o último de sua linhagem familiar, morrendo sem um herdeiro que continuasse seu legado, e que foi amaldiçoado a continuar o dever de sua família mesmo após a morte. Empunhando a pá retorcida que teve em vida, ele continua seu trabalho macabro, eternamente escavando e preenchendo covas na Ilha das Sombras.','br','6.5.1'),(83,'Yorick','o Coveiro','Ilha das Sombras','Yorick','Uma criatura trágica e aterrorizante, Yorick é um ser fantasmagórico que e